        },
        "step_QLTicL": {
          "type": "step",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "The Sulfur Eliminator destroys existing bad breath",
            "body": "<p>The Sulfur Eliminating Solution immediately destroys any sulfur gas already present in your mouth — giving you instant fresh breath from the first rinse.</p>"
          }
        },
        "step_eqUjgM": {
          "type": "step",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "Zinc ions block germs from producing more",
            "body": "<p>The billions of activated zinc ions bond to the germs in your mouth and prevent them from consuming protein particles. No protein consumption means no sulfur gas production — and no bad breath returning for 12 hours per rinse, 24 hours with two rinses a day.</p>"
